column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, &&&&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.mjd, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
